OL,3,CHow Nigel Farage plans to become PM
OL,5,FThis conference was the first time
OL,6,FReform UK's supporters had gathered
OL,7,Fsince the party secured more than four
OL,8,Fmillion votes - and five MPs - in
OL,9,FJuly's election. It was a chance for
OL,10,Fofficials, volunteers and its
OL,11,Fpoliticians to celebrate. And
OL,12,Fcelebrate they did.
OL,14,FDay one of the conference culminated
OL,15,Fin what one Reform source promised
OL,16,Fwould be "the biggest drinking session
OL,17,Fin British political history." It
OL,18,Ffeatured karaoke from Nigel Farage -
OL,19,Fhilarious or horrifying depending on
OL,20,Fyour view.
