OL,3,CHow Nigel Farage plans to become PM
OL,5,FBefore that, each of the party's new
OL,6,FMPs spoke to an adoring crowd of four
OL,7,Fthousand people. The Ashfield MP Lee
OL,8,FAnderson got the biggest laughs. Nigel
OL,9,FFarage (saving his singing until
OL,10,Flater) got the biggest cheers.
OL,12,FThe speeches weren't much different
OL,13,Ffrom what we heard during the general
OL,14,Felection a few months earlier. But
OL,15,Fnobody seemed to notice or care.
OL,16,F"We're playing the hits," said a
OL,17,Fsenior Reform source.
