OL,3,CHow Nigel Farage plans to become PM
OL,5,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,6,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,7,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,8,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,10,FDay two of the conference was more low-
OL,11,Fprofile but far more significant. As
OL,12,Fdelegates nursed their hangovers, they
OL,13,Fapproved a new constitution (a handful
OL,14,Fof people in the hall opposed it, not
OL,15,Fthat the vote had any real meaning).
OL,16,FIt means Nigel Farage will, in time,
OL,17,Fgive up his controlling stake in the
OL,18,Fparty, giving members the ability to
OL,19,Fremove him as leader.
