OL,3,CHow Nigel Farage plans to become PM
OL,5,FFarage told ITV News that "loopy" and
OL,6,F"extremely racist" Reform UK
OL,7,Fcandidates caused his party "enormous
OL,8,Fdamage" at the last election. "And
OL,9,Fprobably rightly so," he added. For
OL,10,Fthis reason, he wants to
OL,11,F"professionalise" the party, setting
OL,12,Fup local branches, a party board, and
OL,13,Fcrucially, a better vetting process
OL,14,Ffor candidates.
