OL,3,CHow Nigel Farage plans to become PM
OL,5,FHe spoke about his desire to emulate
OL,6,Fthe Liberal Democrats campaigning
OL,7,Ftactics, and hopes members will leave
OL,8,Fthis conference ready to knock on
OL,9,Fdoors and gather data ahead of next
OL,10,Fyear's local elections - where in
OL,11,FEngland Farage hopes his party can win
OL,12,Fhundreds of seats.
OL,14,FThat is the first staging post over
OL,15,Fthe next four years as Reform aims to
OL,16,Fbecome a party of government. The
OL,17,Fsuccess - or failure - of the plans to
OL,18,Fmodernise, professionalise and
OL,19,Fdemocratise Reform UK will determine
OL,20,Fwhether Nigel Farage achieves his
OL,21,Fambition of becoming prime minister.
